{"tid":1886687,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓一日暴增15單武漢肺炎","createTime":"2020-02-19T05:17:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T06:24:19.000Z","uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"41cf6983b5b115e4ec43a8a6ceebdf1745ac8309","tid":1886687,"uid":154277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:17:45.000Z","msg":"韓國今（19）日通報出現15例新增COVID-19（2019冠狀病毒疾病，簡稱「武漢肺炎」）感染病例，累計確診病例達46例，其中有13例出現在大邱和慶北地區，都與一間教會的聚會有關。<br />\n<br />\n《韓聯社》報導，韓國中央防疫對策本部上午表示，新增15例中，有13例發生在大邱市和慶尚北道地區，其中11例曾與此前確診的第31例患者接觸，當中有10人是透過教堂，1人是醫院接觸者。<br />\n<br />\n其他地區發生的2例確診病例中，一例是11歲的女童，其父母此前已先後確診，在居家隔離中出現疑似症狀並接受檢測後結果呈陽性，也是韓國首例的兒童感染病例。另一名則是居住在首爾市城東區的77歲韓國男性，沒有海外旅行史，也未曾接觸其他病例。該2例患者目前已轉入定點醫院接受隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\n而隨著確診病例的暴增，位於大邱的慶北大學醫院和啟明大學東山醫療院等醫療機構急診室紛紛關閉。<br />\n<br />\n《風傳媒》報導，位於大邱的慶北大學醫院表示，院內有患者被檢查出新型冠狀病毒（2019-nCOV）陽性，18日晚間院長親自下令封鎖急診室。<br />\n<br />\n感染途徑不明，韓國疫情進入新局面<br />\n<br />\n傳染給10多人的31例確診患者，是第三大城市大邱市的一名61歲女子。《明報》報導，她2月6日早上因遇上交通意外，翌日入院留醫，2月8日發燒，2月14日診斷為肺炎，2月18日確診新型冠狀病毒肺炎。<br />\n<br />\n連同在16日確診的首爾另2名確診夫婦，截至18日韓國所謂「不特定感染」確診者增加到了3人。韓國疾病管理本部長鄭銀敬在18日的例行記者會上表示：「（像這3個人一樣）很難確認在哪裡感染的患者，有可能進一步增加，因此武漢冠狀病毒正在迎來新的局面。」<br />\n<br />\n韓國官方今日將召開記者會，詳細說明大邱暴增的感染案例情形。<br />\n<br />\n然而，她留院期間連續2個周日參加教會崇拜，15日又到酒店出席一場婚宴和相關的酒店自助午餐。與她同期的住院患者有33人，教會崇拜涉及數百人，婚宴午餐會場更有逾1000人，惹人擔心她可能成為「超級傳播者」。<br />\n<br />\n《朝鮮日報》18日報導指出，此患者最近從未去過國外，也從未與其他確診患者接觸過，無法得知是如何被感染的。<br />\n<br />\n醬：<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/131449?fbclid=IwAR0YtkptQ_AiusBFG3_lXMx6Z7Q63-HbVHc3yK3ADbROuF81RzZ4IB0mCc8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F131449%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0YtkptQ_AiusBFG3_lXMx6Z7Q63-HbVHc3yK3ADbROuF81RzZ4IB0mCc8&d=WZLdF6k3LRQ%2Bb7h5E4OoDiBot4r0pQQ4M2eut5PfJzM%3D&h=c1037cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/131449?fbclid=IwAR0YtkptQ_AiusBFG3_lXMx6Z7Q63-HbVHc3yK3ADbROuF81RzZ4IB0mCc8</a>"},{"pid":"7d328c25e62daadbd0688e532e6a3a57a05bbbd0","tid":1886687,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/depYbMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdepYbMJ.jpg&h=b63851ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e01af04b66f770df1c1b56a.jpg/xpaqoEMDJwIfkmoNEyptE-udQxKDyF8zg33NY4N9zWM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e01af04b66f770df1c1b56a.jpg%2FxpaqoEMDJwIfkmoNEyptE-udQxKDyF8zg33NY4N9zWM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0afa68d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"02e771f6d100cf9f492ac632ad881f36b188ed3d","tid":1886687,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7d328c25e62daadbd0688e532e6a3a57a05bbbd0","tid":1886687,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/depYbMJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdepYbMJ.jpg&h=b63851ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5e01af04b66f770df1c1b56a.jpg/xpaqoEMDJwIfkmoNEyptE-udQxKDyF8zg33NY4N9zWM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5e01af04b66f770df1c1b56a.jpg%2FxpaqoEMDJwIfkmoNEyptE-udQxKDyF8zg33NY4N9zWM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=0afa68d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:13:47.000Z","msg":"真‧有難同當<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e49714d7b08b11278196a612d38bd0f1760b9ab2","tid":1886687,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T06:16:45.000Z","msg":"以為只係首爾先有例<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"007a6a44b01a9c4dd64b7fc9807390e582d982d5","tid":1886687,"uid":329698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"